http://training.skillo-bg.com:4200/posts/create

1. Locator for Drop an Image container
CSS: div.uploadfilecontainer
XPath: //div[contains(@class, "uploadfilecontainer")]

2. Locator for Drop an Image input field
CSS: div.uploadfilecontainer>input
XPath: //div[contains(@class, "uploadfilecontainer")]/input

3. Locator for Drop an Image label
CSS: div.uploadfilecontainer>label
XPath: //div[contains(@class, "uploadfilecontainer")]/label

4. Locator for Browse button
CSS: #choose-file
XPath: //button[@id='choose-file']

5. Locator for Caption input field
CSS: input[formcontrolname='caption']
XPath: //input[@formcontrolname="caption"]

6. Locator for Private-public switch
CSS: #customSwitch2
XPath: //input[@id='customSwitch2']

7. Locator for Private label
CSS: div.input-group-addon label:first-child
XPath: //div[contains(@class, "input-group-addon")]//label[1]

8. Locator for Public label
CSS: div.input-group-addon label:nth-of-type(2)
XPath: //div[contains(@class, "input-group-addon")]//label[last()]

9. Locator for Submit button
CSS: #create-post
XPath: //button[@id="create-post"]

10. Locator for iSkillo icon button
CSS: #homeIcon
XPath: //img[@id='homeIcon']

11. Locator for Home button
CSS: #nav-link-home
XPath: //a[@id='nav-link-home']

12. Locator for Profile button
CSS: #nav-link-profile
XPath: //a[@id='nav-link-profile']

13. Locator for New post button
CSS: #nav-link-new-post
XPath: //a[@id='nav-link-new-post']

14. Locator for Search input bar
CSS: #search-bar
XPath: //input[@id='search-bar']

15. Locator for Search button
CSS: i.fas.fa-search
XPath: //i[@class='fas fa-search']

16. Locator for Sign-out button
CSS: i.fas.fa-sign-out-alt
XPath: //i[@class='fas fa-sign-out-alt fa-lg']

